      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[\"B\"(z,w) = int_0^1 t^(z-1)(1-t)^(w-1) \"d\"t]\n\n(for stem:[\"Re \"z > 0], stem:[\"Re \"w > 0])\n\nstem:[rm(B)(z,w) = Gamma(z) Gamma(w) // Gamma(z+w)]\n\nstem:[1/((n+1)rm(B)(k+1,n-k+1))= ((n),(k))] (for stem:[k <= n])\n",
